<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name viewport="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Me</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN for easy styling -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- Google Fonts - Inter -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            /* Applying a vibrant gradient background with the requested colors */
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF69B4, #8A2BE2, #00BFFF, #DC143C); /* Pink, Blue Violet, Deep Sky Blue, Crimson */
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1rem; /* Add some padding around the edges */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-white">
    <!-- Main container for the content, centered and styled -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl w-full bg-white bg-opacity-10 backdrop-filter backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl shadow-2xl p-8 md:p-12 space-y-8 flex flex-col items-center">

        <!-- Header Section -->
        <header class="text-center w-full">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-shadow-lg drop-shadow-md">Hello, I'm [Your Name]!</h1>
            <p class="text-xl font-light opacity-90">Welcome to my little corner of the web.</p>
        </header>

        <!-- Main Content Section -->
        <main class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-8 w-full">
            <!-- Image Section -->
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <!-- Placeholder for your image. Replace 'width' and 'height' and the URL with your actual image. -->
                <!-- Use a square image for best results, e.g., 300x300 -->
                <img src="https://placehold.co/300x300/ff69b4/ffffff?text=Your+Photo"
                     alt="A photo of [Your Name]"
                     class="rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-lg w-48 h-48 md:w-64 md:h-64 object-cover"
                     onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='https://placehold.co/300x300/ff69b4/ffffff?text=Image+Not+Found';">
            </div>

            <!-- Introduction Text Section -->
            <section class="flex-grow text-lg leading-relaxed text-center md:text-left">
                <p class="mb-4">
                    Hi there! I'm delighted to share a bit about myself with you. I am passionate about [Your Passion/Field], and I love exploring [Your Hobby/Interest].
                </p>
                <p class="mb-4">
                    My journey has led me through [mention a key experience or two, e.g., fascinating projects, unique learning experiences, or significant achievements]. I believe in [Your Core Belief/Value].
                </p>
                <p>
                    Outside of [Your Professional Area], you can often find me [describe a favorite pastime, e.g., reading a good book, hiking in nature, or experimenting with new recipes]. I'm excited to connect and learn more about you!
                </p>
            </section>
        </main>

        <!-- Footer Section -->
        <footer class="text-center text-sm opacity-80 mt-8 w-full">
            <p>&copy; 2024 [Your Name]. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
